### BOOKING TESTS (Customer)
### Requires: {{TOKEN}} to be a valid, unexpired JWT for a user with role 'customer'
### -------------------------------------------------------------

@bookingId=0

### (1) Create Booking
POST {{BASE}}/api/customer/booking
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
	"packageid": 3,
	"eventdate": "2027-12-25",
	"eventtime": "10:30:00",
	"eventaddress": "123 Test Avenue, Sample City",
	"contact_info": "09171234567",
	"notes": "Christmas shoot"
}



### (2) Edit Booking (allowed fields: packageid, eventaddress, contact_info, notes)
###change 4 to actual bookingId from response of (1) above
PATCH {{BASE}}/api/customer/booking/4
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
	"packageid": 4,
	"eventaddress": "456 Updated Venue Road, New City",
	"contact_info": "09179876543",
	"notes": "Updated: indoor studio instead"
}

### (3) Cancel Booking
DELETE {{BASE}}/api/customer/booking/{{bookingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### (4) Negative Test - Attempt to edit cancelled booking (should fail)
PATCH {{BASE}}/api/customer/booking/{{bookingId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
	"notes": "Trying to edit after cancel"
}

